::DarkMouse/KitKat::

DarkMouse::
Returns to base.  She walks in and finds a wolf in her chair. She 
walkes up to her console. "May I help you? Your sitting in my seat."

KitKat::
"Yeah, I know.  I was just watching the scanners.  About time you 
guys got back.  Quickstrike has been wanting to talk to you since you 
left with Megatron."

DarkMouse::
"Yeah, well," Looks at KitKat. "Take your feet off my console.  
That's highly specialized equipment."

KitKat:: 
Puts her feet down off the console. "Ok, OK, OK. I'll watch it from 
now on. But go and see Quickstrike.  Oh, wait.  Better let him and 
Stringtra finish first."

DarkMouse::
"OK. I'll wait." She walked around and looked at the screens.
"Nothing yet huh?"

KitKat:
"Nope, nothing yet."

DarkMouse::
She was getting annouyed that this wolfbot would just come i and take 
over her position at her console. 
"Don't you have something to go and do right now?"

KitKat::
"Right now?"

DarkMouse::
"Yes, right now."

KitKat::
Looks at the mouse.  Realizes that she may have stepped into the 
mouse's terratory. She gave in. No reason to fight, not over a 
computer. "Yeah, I got stuff to do. Cya around Darkmouse."  She 
walked over to a corner of the cave where she could watch the room.

DarkMouse::
She went around the console and sat down.  She saw that KitKat hasd 
been tampering with the computer and she smiled. "Ha, that wolf 
couldn't get in." She started fworking on her programms for the 
systems.
